snippet.title: Stumble upon Rumble Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Finally, our new game trailer is here!

We are super excited to share this with you all. The trailer features some of our top features:
- Of course our 100% skill-based fighting
- Player-to-Player token fights
- NFT cosmetics
- Social focused
- Community representation

The trailer was made by Alexandr Slyusarev, who has worked for other top gaming brands like Ubisoft, Sony Pictures, Twitch, Amazon and more.

If you haven't already, make sure you check out our other channels:

Website: https://stumbleuponrumble.com
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/ckDM6GJX4m
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StumbleURumble
Medium: https://stumbleuponrumble.medium.com

See you there!
